data.description: Open concept with an abundance of natural light in our beloved '05! New price and major updates, assuring peace of mind for many, many years. From the huge master bedroom boasting a sizable en suite with separate shower and jetted tub to the brand new tear-off roof with 50 year GAF dimensional shingles (June 2023), this charming home across from Northside park has so much to offer. With updated electrical, windows, siding, and kitchen in addition to the new furnace & central air (2021), water heater (2021), and new mud room entry door (2023), there is very little for the new owner to do but move in and make it their own. HVAC system includes built-in Remi-Halo ionized air purifier and 10-year transferrable warranty and Ecobee app-controlled smart thermostat. The current owner also recently had the main sewer line sealed after having a huge tree removed from the fenced-in back yard beside the extended 1-car detached garage. Seller offering a $5000 credit for costs/cosmetics!
